trans-unit.source: Serves as the primary control in the Web Parts control set for hosting <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls on a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Fungerer som den primære kontrollen i webdeler kontrollen som er angitt for vert <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> vises på en webside.

trans-unit.source: Within the Web Parts control set, a zone is a composite control that covers a defined region on a Web page and contains server controls.
trans-unit.target: En sone er en sammensatt kontroll som dekker et angitt område på en webside og inneholder serverkontroller i settet webdeler kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The primary functions of a zone are to lay out the controls it contains, and to provide a common user interface (UI) for those controls.
trans-unit.target: De primære funksjonene i en sone er å sette opp Kontroller den inneholder, og oppgi en vanlig brukergrensesnittet (UI) for kontrollene.

trans-unit.source: For general information about zones and how they are used in Web Parts applications, see the reference documentation for the base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone> class, and [Web Parts Control Set Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha generell informasjon om soner og hvordan de brukes i webdeler programmer, kan du se referansedokumentasjonen for grunntallet <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone>klassen, og [deler kontrollen angitt oversikt over Web](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone>

trans-unit.source: The EditorZone control is one of the fundamental controls in the Web Parts control set.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen EditorZone er én av de grunnleggende kontrollene i webdeler kontrollen settet.

trans-unit.source: A key feature of Web Parts is the ability of end users to modify (or personalize) Web pages according to their preferences, and save their personalized settings for future browser sessions.
trans-unit.target: En nøkkel funksjon i webdeler er muligheten for sluttbrukerne mulighet til å endre (eller tilpasse) nettsider i henhold til innstillingene og lagre sine personlige innstillinger for fremtidige nettleseren økter.

trans-unit.source: One aspect of modifying Web Parts pages includes editing; users can edit the appearance, layout, behavior, and other properties of the visible <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: En side ved å endre webdeler sidene inneholder redigere; brukere kan redigere utseendet, oppsett, virkemåte og andre egenskaper for det vises <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Several controls in the Web Parts control set provide the editing features, including the EditorZone control.
trans-unit.target: Flere kontroller i webdeler kontrollen settet angi redigering funksjoner, inkludert kontrollen EditorZone.

trans-unit.source: An EditorZone control becomes visible when a Web Parts page enters edit mode, and it makes available various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls that can be used to personalize <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: En kontroll som EditorZone blir synlig når en webdeler side går inn i redigeringsmodus, og den blir tilgjengelig ulike <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontrollene som kan brukes til å tilpasse <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The EditorZone control is very similar to its parent, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> class, with one key difference: The EditorZone control provides a zone template, referenced in its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen EditorZone ligner overordnet i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>klassen med en viktig forskjell: kontrollen i EditorZone gir en zone-mal, som det refereres til i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.ZoneTemplate%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>

trans-unit.source: The zone template adds the ability to declare content in the page persistence format.
trans-unit.target: Malen sone legger muligheten til å deklarere i siden utholdenhet-format.

trans-unit.source: Page developers can place an EditorZone control in the declarative markup of a Web page, add a child `<zonetemplate>` element, and within the `<zonetemplate>` element, add declarative references to <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Siden utviklere kan plassere en kontroll som EditorZone i deklarerende koden for en webside, Legg til en underordnet `<zonetemplate>` element, og i den `<zonetemplate>` element, legge til deklarerende referanser til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The EditorZone control also has a method, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.CreateEditorParts%2A>, which overrides a base method in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> class.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen EditorZone også er en metode <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.CreateEditorParts%2A>, som overstyrer en base metode i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone.CreateEditorParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: This method is necessary so that an EditorZone control can create the zone template to contain any <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls that are added to the zone declaratively.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden er nødvendig slik at en kontroll som EditorZone kan opprette zone-malen til å inneholde <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller som er lagt til i sonen deklarativt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The buttons in the EditorZone UI require client-side scripting in order to work correctly.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Knappene EditorZone UI krever klientside for å fungere på riktig måte.

trans-unit.source: If scripting is disabled in the browser, the user will not be able to perform actions through the EditorZone UI.
trans-unit.target: Hvis skripting er deaktivert i nettleseren, er ikke brukeren kan utføre handlinger ved hjelp av EditorZone UI.

trans-unit.source: Accessibility The markup rendered by default for this control might not conform to accessibility standards such as the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines 1.0 (WCAG) priority 1 guidelines.
trans-unit.target: Tilgjengelighet markup gjengis som standard for denne kontrollen, kan ikke med kravene for tilgjengelighet standarder som Web innhold tilgjengelighet retningslinjene 1.0 (WCAG) prioritet 1 retningslinjene.

trans-unit.source: For details about accessibility support for this control, see [ASP.NET Controls and Accessibility](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om tilgjengelighet støtte for denne kontrollen, kan du se [ASP.NET-kontroller og tilgjengelighet](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Creates all the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls declared within a zone template in page persistence format.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter alle de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> Kontroller deklarert i en mal for sonen siden utholdenhet format.

trans-unit.source: The CreateEditorParts method overrides the base method to create only the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls that are declared within the zone template.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateEditorParts overstyrer base-metoden til å opprette bare den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller som er deklarert i malen sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: Any other <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls added to the zone must be added programmatically.
trans-unit.target: Alle andre <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontrollene er lagt til i sonen må legges til programmatisk.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: This can be done, for example, by implementing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable> interface in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Dette kan gjøres, for eksempel ved å implementere den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable>grensesnitt i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable>

trans-unit.source: Then, in the overridden <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A> method, you can add a collection of custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls to a zone.
trans-unit.target: Deretter i den overstyrte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>metoden, kan du legge til en samling med egendefinerte <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller til en sone.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.IWebEditable.CreateEditorParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"></xref> that contains references to all the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> controls declared within the zone template.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartCollection"> </xref> som inneholder referanser til alle de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> Kontroller deklarert i zone-malen.

trans-unit.source: The current <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control does not have an ID.
trans-unit.target: Gjeldende <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontrollen ikke har en ID.

trans-unit.source: Provides a template to contain child controls within an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone"></xref> control in page persistence format.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en mal for å inneholde underordnede kontroller i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone"> </xref> kontroll på sider utholdenhet.

trans-unit.source: The ZoneTemplate property is the key difference between the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> class and the base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> class.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ZoneTemplate er den største forskjellen mellom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>klassen og base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>

trans-unit.source: By adding support for a zone template, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> class enables page developers to place child <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls within an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> control in the declarative markup of a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Ved å legge til støtte for en mal for sonen den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>klassen aktiverer siden utviklere å plassere underordnede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontrollerer i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>kontrollen i deklarerende koden for en webside.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>

trans-unit.source: The zone template acts as a container for the child controls.
trans-unit.target: Malen sone fungerer som en beholder for underordnede-kontroller.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The set accessor for the ZoneTemplate property calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.InvalidateEditorParts%2A> method, which forces the collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls declared in the template to be recreated.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Sett aksessor for ZoneTemplate egenskapen kall av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.InvalidateEditorParts%2A>metode, som tvinger samlingen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller deklarert i malen skal opprettes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase.InvalidateEditorParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: This causes any changes in the contents of the template to be recognized.
trans-unit.target: Dette gjør endringer i innholdet i malen som skal gjenkjennes.

trans-unit.source: To use a zone template declaratively within an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> control, you add a pair of `<zonetemplate>` tags, and reference <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls between the tags.
trans-unit.target: Bruke en mal for sonen deklarativt i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>kontroll, du legge til et par `<zonetemplate>` koder og referanse <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>Kontroller mellom kodene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>

trans-unit.source: Only one zone template is rendered per instance of an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> control (therefore, there is no reason to add multiple `<zonetemplate>` elements to an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> control).
trans-unit.target: Bare én sone malen gjengis per forekomst av en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>kontrollen (det er derfor ingen grunn til å legge til flere `<zonetemplate>` elementer til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>kontrollen).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>

trans-unit.source: Also, the zone template of an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone> control can contain only part controls that derive from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> class.
trans-unit.target: Også zone-mal for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>kontroll kan inneholde bare Delkontroller som avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZone>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.ITemplate"></xref> zone template that acts as a container for child controls in the zone.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.ITemplate"> </xref> zone-malen som fungerer som en beholder for underordnede kontroller i sonen.
